NAME
       bal mi - Ballerina WSO2 Micro Integrator Tool

SYNOPSIS
       bal mi [OPTIONS] [<arguments>]

DESCRIPTION
       The 'bal mi' command-line tool generates WSO2 Micro Integrator connector to execute Ballerina transformation.

OPTIONS
       -i, --input <ballerina project>
           Path to Ballerina project that includes the transformation logic.

EXAMPLES
       Generate WSO2 micro integrator connector for Ballerina.
           $ bal mi -i ballerina/project
